The Lord God made them all.<br>
 <br>
Each nasty little hornet,<br>
Each beastly little squid,<br>
Who made the spiky urchin?<br>
Who made the sharks? He did!<br>
 <br>
All things scant and ulcerous,<br>
All pox both great and small,<br>
Putrid, foul and gangrenous,<br>
The Lord God made them all.<br>
